{"tid":360684,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"紋身大隻男打贏架　向中年漢遞紙巾示好","createTime":"2017-08-15T13:23:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-15T16:32:14.000Z","uid":28765,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"073d1188a4ccf05ccddab844117a0ca58e9c0437","tid":360684,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T13:23:36.000Z","msg":"男人間解決紛爭，或許是來一場「隻揪」，勝方不驕，敗者不餒，完場後拍拍膊頭當無數。今日傍晚在黃大仙一條行人隧道，兩名彪形大漢因身體碰撞發生爭執，肥材中年漢向對方挑機，指手劃腳疑要「隻揪」，健碩的紋身漢即放下背囊，脫去上衣，赤膊應戰。雙方大打出手，惟中年漢不敵對方重拳，被打至倒地，左眼紅腫瘀傷。大戰過後，兩人由講手到最後講和，紋身漢遞上紙巾安慰，一場猶如「男人的浪漫」的拳頭戰落幕。<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.jobmarket.tw/bbs/attachment.php?s=6bc002122e237d31f83e218f7185485d&amp;attachmentid=3316&amp;d=1378919526\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jobmarket.tw%2Fbbs%2Fattachment.php%3Fs%3D6bc002122e237d31f83e218f7185485d%26attachmentid%3D3316%26d%3D1378919526&h=8072f0dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vKT0XctKYFU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DvKT0XctKYFU&d=SyyntnPjcMaXdtaaHlF8%2BQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=629731f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vKT0XctKYFU</a>"},{"pid":"8aa739afa3dc7b82ae9c46776193df5e207a1850","tid":360684,"uid":16910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T13:25:04.000Z","msg":"ip 都唔駛check 竹園"},{"pid":"30e3cf760007f43f3e850f55a1df7774297efb75","tid":360684,"uid":74145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T13:26:40.000Z","msg":"個呀叔係咪比人打到隻眼腫曬😂😂"},{"pid":"e17ab180a769aeb25f9744ebb977f86e00690865","tid":360684,"uid":34993,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T13:28:43.000Z","msg":"阿叔佢就敢恰<br />\n鈍到咁遇著D學過一兩年既收硬皮"},{"pid":"795805506bf313e626fb6b7691639254fa87cf87","tid":360684,"uid":60959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T13:29:05.000Z","msg":"香港一早應用推動決鬥法"},{"pid":"6f41ed1c1d8aefc748e7ddb5f78209de7c7d86af","tid":3606